        <item>
            <title>【教學】AI 執相修圖 Google Gemini 2.0 Flash，輸入文字即可 PS 圖片毋須技術</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/google-gemini-ai-2/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=google-gemini-ai-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/google-gemini-ai-2/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 11:56:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Google Gemini]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1297625</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Google Gemini 2.0 Flash 推出了一段時間，但一直僅限部分人測試，最近 Google 終於開放。目前 Gemini 2.0 flash 已推出 Experimental 版本，能夠生成圖片，基本上你輸入指令就可以替你修改圖片。現在就讓小編和大家一起試玩這個新功能吧！</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031451511-467x580.jpg" alt="" width="467" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031451511-467x580.jpg 467w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031451511.jpg 724w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 467px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一句即可幫你改顏色</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297671" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031463541-466x580.jpg" alt="" width="466" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031463541-466x580.jpg 466w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031463541.jpg 723w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 466px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲也可生成可愛卡通</p><h2>需求</h2><p>VPN</p><h2>Step 1 登入 Google 帳戶</h2><p>開啟 VPN 之後，點擊下面連結進入 Google Gemini 2.0 頁面，再點擊「Try in Google AI Studio」，然後你就可以登入你的 Google 帳戶。</p><p>連結：<a href="https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/flash/">https://deepmind.google/technologies/gemini/flash/</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297630" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031451945-694x371.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="371" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031451945-694x371.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025031451945.jpg 1097w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「Try in Google AI Studio」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1297631" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_5_21_31-694x353.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="353" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_5_21_31-694x353.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/20250314_5_21_31.jpg 929w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲登入 Google 帳戶</p><br /><b>
]]>
