        </item>
        <item>
            <title>華為下週四舉行新 Pura 發佈會，傳發佈 Flip 3 摺疊手機熒幕或採新展開方式</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/huawei-rumored-launch-flip-3-foldable-phone-next-thu-screen-size-similar-to-ipad-mini/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-rumored-launch-flip-3-foldable-phone-next-thu-screen-size-similar-to-ipad-mini</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/14/huawei-rumored-launch-flip-3-foldable-phone-next-thu-screen-size-similar-to-ipad-mini/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 14 Mar 2025 03:00:55 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Flip 3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei]]>
